{"tid":2301802,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"窗邊行動再起","createTime":"2020-11-26T14:47:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T13:00:24.000Z","uid":293624,"like":20,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"396df840188c329e783a97675d407f69590b347e","tid":2301802,"uid":293624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T14:47:27.000Z","msg":"今時今日場運動已經冷卻左落黎，大部分人縱使並未忘記及麻木，但一定迷茫到唔知可以做d乜。今日我終於作出行動，於9時正於窗邊播放香港國歌「願榮光歸香港」，希望大家可以由聽日開始再次發動窗邊行動，一齊於晚上9時正用各自方法，於家中向街道一起播放香港國歌，令香港人嘅聲音響徹全港，務求重新喚醒香港人，繼續保持抗爭意志。<br />\n<br />\n最後一句，光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"689b2e96de8635b183e6c1c2265a7fa45e357b6d","tid":2301802,"uid":293624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T14:54:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a7af300dc96a58b03dbbc26cb0f2f95bad68394e","tid":2301802,"uid":293624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T14:57:34.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"ccf0e43ae6e72f809632065c572e2311364fce90","tid":2301802,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T01:46:56.000Z","msg":"Oushhhh"},{"pid":"59c8096c3ae6d75349870b00c8ba7e0ed9319a14","tid":2301802,"uid":290118,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T02:02:28.000Z","msg":"十點鳩叫<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iytbDOG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiytbDOG.png&h=ad1f8f49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef92bbd382155f79e4c464a3384276e18b8f186a","tid":2301802,"uid":293624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T13:04:42.000Z","msg":"再自推，推到有人同行為止。"},{"pid":"ec4a7f03c474aaca36ecd43135526dfc5b6f1cc8","tid":2301802,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T13:05:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22afd68e87b5f70740d92fb1c0989a10fdf86e92","tid":2301802,"uid":139588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T13:05:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1aa0d5e327ac679bca8f73c25e39a27902001172","tid":2301802,"uid":293624